                                sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                text="&lt;p>Our Employee Resource Groups (ERGs) help foster a diverse and inclusive environment that empowers everyone to bring their best selves to work each day. It drives innovation through collaboration and openness to ideas that emerge from each person’s unique life experiences. It helps us have greater empathy with our patients, customers, and communities we serve. It’s our commitment to supporting people to thrive and creating a more equitable and inclusive workplace for all.&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;Watch the below video to learn more.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
