                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                            text="&lt;p>We value diverse perspectives, creating an inclusive culture and treating all employees with dignity and respect. When everyone can be themselves at work and when they’re treated with respect and dignity, we maximise every employee’s potential.&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;Equity, Equality, Diversity, and Inclusion are at the heart of how we “do good business.” It’s more than a commitment—it’s who we are. Hear from Carla as she shares what this role means to her and&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;/content/abbvie-com2/nz/en/who-we-are/our-stories/nurturing-inclusivity-and-belonging-at-abbVie-australia.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>read more here&lt;/a>&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                            textIsRich="true"/>
